comments: Young cool teacher - she\'s the kind of teacher that you respect a lot, but at the same time she\'s funny and on the student\'s level which is nice. She\'s very approachable and is good at helping before/after class and via email. She\'s VERY passionate about her class which rubs off on most students. Over all GREAT.

Emily Carman is very experienced in the ways of film. she makes it very interesting and she is just a fun person! she does grade somewhat hard so be prepared for that. other than that she is fair and genuinely cares about the class.
